rtists/beam">BEAM</a>一起出现在歌曲“Make A W”中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aj-tracey-teases-big-features-on-funky-and-dancehall-inspired-new-album-3773018">AJ Tracey 后调侃“funky”和受舞厅启发的新专辑的“大特色”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
